

Language API :
----------------

READ :
    curl -i -H "Accept: application/json" -X GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/language
    curl -i -H "Accept: application/json" -X GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/language/xx/

CREATE :
    curl -i -H "Accept: application/json" -X POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/language -d "code=br&name=brazil&lname=brazil&charset=utf-8"
    
UPDATE :
    curl -i -H "Accept: application/json" -X PUT http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/language/br/ -d "name=Brazilian"
    
DELETE :
    curl -i -H "Accept: application/json" -X DELETE http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/language/br/
    
    
